<%- include('../partials/html-head') %>
<%- include('../partials/nav') %>

<h1><%= title %></h1>
<div>
  <form id="add-recipe-form" action="/recipes/<%= recipe._id %>?_method=PUT" method="POST">
    <div id="add-recipe-summary">
      <h4>Add Recipe</h4>
      <p>Welcome to your crafting page. This is your space, this is where you make the magic
        happen, this is where you make a bunch of people happy. Make your recipe here like a 
        CHEF, share it with your friends and other users, update and delete it whenever you please.
      </p>
      <hr>
    </div>

    <div id="title-description">
      <div id="title-description-fields">
        <div>
          <label for="recipe-title">Recipe Title</label>
          <input id="recipe-title" type="text" name="title" placeholder="recipe title here" required value="<%= recipe.title %>">
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="recipe-description">Description</label>
          <input id="recipe-description" type="text" name="description" placeholder="recipe title here" value="<%= recipe.description %>">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- <div id="recipe-ingredients">
      <h4>Ingredients</h4>
      <p>Carefully choose the indispensable elements of your craft in this section. 
        Be mindful of items you pick because ultimately they define the taste of the 
        dish you end up making, and of course you want it to be tasty!
      </p>
      <input id="recipe-ingredient" name="ingredients" type="text" placeholder="Add your ingredients here" >
    </div> -->

    <div id="recipe-directions">
      <h4>Directions</h4>
      <p>Here that section where you get to reveal to the world the secrets of your craft!
        They say good artists never reveal their tricks. But we believe differently, we believe 
        that sharing is what empower us to receive too. Now has come your time to share the roadmap
        to culinary perfection.
      </p>
      <input id="recipe-direction" name="directions" type="text" placeholder="Add a step here" value="<%= recipe.directions %>">
    </div>

    <!-- <div id="public-private">
      <h4>Make this recipe public?</h4>
      <input type="radio" name="postType" id="public-toggle" value="public">
      <label for="postType" ></label>
      <div><span>Anyone who sees my profile can see this recipe</span></div>
      <input type="radio" id="private-toggle" name="postType" value="private" >
      <label for="private-toggle">Personal Recipes</label>
      <div><span>Only I can see the recipe</span></div>
    </div> -->

    <div id="cancel-submit">
      <button>Cancel</button>
      <button type="submit">Edit Recipe</button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

